  The heavy gates rest open, welcoming all those who wish to master the
realm of Northern Crossroads.  Within these walls you will follow in the
footsteps of the most skilled mudders of NC.  Our trainers will see that
you learn ALL you need to know to develop into a powerful force in this
realm. 
  You can look at the sign here by typing: 'look sign' or 'l sign' 
  To begin your training, go north by typing: 'north' or just 'n'.
   
