{BO}{BLU}Inside the Gates{blu}~
   
  As you pass through the gates a broad warrior shoves you to the side 
and promptly exits.  AHH!  You would love to kick in that guy's face, 
but you know better than to try it without any training.  Luckily, your 
fall is broken by a large wooden table.  Upon the table is a stack of 
manuals which all new trainees must study and master. Be sure to pick 
up one for yourself.
   
  As you survey the open courtyard you see several new trainees resting
next to a large dragonfountain.  An elder mage is lecturing them on the 
different channels in which one's magic can be drawn.
  You can continue onward by going north.  Type: 'n'.  
    
